For all those champions, (wich is like the majority of mages) in the game, 400 mana is about 4, maybe 5 and in some cases like ahri maybe 6 spells. So with about 4-5 spells you used all the mana provided by morello, who used to be the main source of mana for many mages, and that mana wont come back since you have no regen to back it up.

So unless we get extreme buffs to their mana/mana regen or get their costs down by a lot, the mana changes are a nerf to mages in general.

